thread.title: Political backlash escalates over Defence land grab
thread.title_full: Political backlash escalates over Defence land grab

author: ABC Radio National
title: Political backlash escalates over Defence land grab
text:
Image: US marines prepare for a live-fire exercise in bushland in the Shoalwater Bay military training area, near Rockhampton (ABC Open: Lisa Clarke) 
National Party Leader Barnaby Joyce is being urged to back farmers against an ADF land grab for expanded war games. 
The Federal Agriculture Minister will visit Rockhampton on a 'fact-finding' mission as the government faces a growing political backlash over Defence plans to takeover vast swathes of cattle country in central and north Queensland.
